item.title: CVE-2024-6044|2024-06-17T02:30:04.564Z -- d-link -- g403
item.description: Certain models of D-Link wireless routers have a path traversal vulnerability. Unauthenticated attackers on the same local area network can read arbitrary system files by manipulating the URL.
